<help general script_cmds>

These commands are only valid in rooms that have special
scripts written to handle them.  It is likely it won't be
entirely obvious how or where to use them, but builders are
encouraged to give enough clues to allow the thoughtful player
to figure it out.

Commands Supported:  pull, push

Syntax:  CMD [keyword]

Example:  push button
	  pull finger
	  pull 'iron lever'

<color=red>
See Also:  look, examine, add_mob_script
</color></help>
